A vast, glowing cyberpunk cityscape at night where towering neon-lit vending machines replace skyscrapers, each dispensing floating holographic software cubes and data packages into streams of light that flow like rivers between buildings. Tiny drones carry glowing parcels through the electric purple and cyan atmosphere, while massive pipeline networks connect the vending towers, pulsing with energy as packages travel through transparent tubes. In the foreground, a sleek robotic hand reaches up to catch a descending luminescent cube. The scene has deep shadows contrasted with vivid neon reflections on wet streets below, creating a sense of endless automated distribution flowing through a digital metropolis.
